- set Use Base Internationalization in project info
- bundle identifier: org.dontpanicapp
- Device orientation: Portrait
- Requires fullscreen
- File->New->File->Strings File InfoPlist.strings and Localize
- Copy icons and strings and set icon pack (use asset catalog and drag the appicon folder to it)
- Targets -> Add capability -> Push notifications
- edit Info.plist to add languages and camera usage:
<key>CFBundleLocalizations</key>
<array>
<string>en</string>
<string>cs</string>
<string>fr</string>
<string>pl</string>
<string>sk</string>
<string>it</string>
<string>es</string>
<string>de</string>
<string>ru</string>
<string>uk</string>
</array>
<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
<string>This app doesn't use camera. It uses QT Multimedia for accessing audio files.</string>
<key>LSMinimumSystemVersion</key>
<string>13.0.0</string>
- LaunchScreen
